org.eclipse.collections.impl.bag.mutable.primitive

Class CharHashBag

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.collections.impl.primitive.AbstractCharIterable
      • org.eclipse.collections.impl.bag.mutable.primitive.CharHashBag
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Externalizable, Serializable, CharBag, MutableCharBag, CharIterable, MutableCharCollection, PrimitiveIterable

    @NotThreadSafe
public final class CharHashBag
extends AbstractCharIterable
implements MutableCharBag, Externalizable
    CharHashBag is similar to HashBag, and is memory-optimized for char primitives. This file was automatically generated from template file primitiveHashBag.stg.
    Since:
    3.0.
